Package model

Class Magazine

java.lang.Object
model.Product
model.Magazine
public class Magazine extends Product
Magazine class represents a magazine product. It extends the Product class and adds additional properties specific to magazines.

    • Magazine

      public Magazine(String name, int pagesAmount, Calendar publishDate, String url, double price, int category, int issueFrecuency)
      Constructs a Magazine object with the given parameters.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the magazine.
      pagesAmount - The number of pages in the magazine.
      publishDate - The publish date of the magazine.
      url - The URL of the magazine.
      price - The price of the magazine.
      category - The category of the magazine (1 for Varieties, 2 for Design, 3 for Scientific).
      issueFrecuency - The issue frequency of the magazine (1 for Diary, 2 for Weekly, 3 for Monthly, 4 for Yearly).
